WEBVTT

00:00:00.056 --> 00:00:45.200
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:06.120
I refuse.

00:01:07.480 --> 00:01:10.319
Our ancestor, Ink Dragon Emperor, was ambushed and killed by the Seven Sins Demon Emperor.

00:01:10.760 --> 00:01:12.719
Our Biluo Shangqing Palace and the Seven Sins Demon Emperor

00:01:12.719 --> 00:01:13.840
have long been mortal enemies.

00:01:14.840 --> 00:01:15.760
Now you want me to

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:17.760
let go of our ancestor's deep grudge

00:01:17.879 --> 00:01:19.719
and bow down to the Seven Sins Demon Emperor?

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:20.959
Impossible.

00:01:22.040 --> 00:01:23.000
Young Palace Master.

00:01:23.439 --> 00:01:25.400
Times have changed.

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:28.760
It's said the Seven Sins Demon Emperor has grown much stronger.

00:01:29.480 --> 00:01:31.760
I'm afraid the Ink Dragon Array

00:01:32.359 --> 00:01:33.840
can no longer stop him.

00:01:34.359 --> 00:01:35.719
If we don't surrender now,

00:01:35.959 --> 00:01:37.799
Biluo Shangqing Palace will be in grave danger.

00:01:38.719 --> 00:01:39.879
Rest assured, Young Palace Master.

00:01:40.159 --> 00:01:41.439
The Seven Sins Demon Emperor said

00:01:41.439 --> 00:01:42.239
as long as you...

00:01:44.760 --> 00:01:45.680
Fine.

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:48.400
So you’ve already sided with the Demon Emperor.

00:01:49.120 --> 00:01:50.799
You’ve always defied me.

00:01:52.120 --> 00:01:53.959
I never wanted to keep you around anyway.

00:01:54.239 --> 00:01:54.840
Guards!

00:01:55.840 --> 00:01:57.599
Seize these traitors!

00:02:00.719 --> 00:02:01.239
Guards!

00:02:03.319 --> 00:02:06.120
The disciples in the palace are getting worse.

00:02:06.879 --> 00:02:09.199
No one even listens to the Young Palace Master anymore.

00:02:09.319 --> 00:02:10.439
Hurry, someone come!

00:02:10.960 --> 00:02:11.560
Let go of me!

00:02:11.680 --> 00:02:12.159
Go!

00:02:12.639 --> 00:02:13.439
Let me go, quickly!

00:02:14.120 --> 00:02:14.639
Palace Master.

00:02:15.439 --> 00:02:17.360
Palace Master, these disciples have all betrayed us.

00:02:19.159 --> 00:02:19.879
Qin Wunian.

00:02:20.719 --> 00:02:22.319
This is where the people's hearts lie.

00:02:22.759 --> 00:02:23.840
If you refuse to surrender,

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:26.439
you’ll drag everyone in Biluo Shangqing Palace down with you.

00:02:26.599 --> 00:02:27.800
How can we let you do that?

00:02:28.319 --> 00:02:30.240
You cowards who fear death

00:02:30.719 --> 00:02:32.240
and betray your own!

00:02:32.719 --> 00:02:35.080
Even if I die here today,

00:02:35.759 --> 00:02:37.120
I’ll fight you to the end!

00:02:48.520 --> 00:02:49.039
Brother Lin.

00:02:49.560 --> 00:02:50.280
Why are you here?

00:02:50.960 --> 00:02:52.039
Sorry you had to witness this.

00:02:52.879 --> 00:02:54.240
The Seven Sins Demon Emperor holds grudges and seeks revenge.

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:56.120
Do you think joining him will save your lives?

00:02:56.520 --> 00:02:57.919
Maybe with another sect, it’s possible.

00:02:58.479 --> 00:03:00.400
But your Biluo Shangqing Palace

00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:02.199
once used the Ink Dragon Array

00:03:02.879 --> 00:03:04.800
to seriously injure the Seven Sins Demon Emperor.

00:03:05.479 --> 00:03:06.800
Not just you disciples,

00:03:07.280 --> 00:03:08.560
even a fly

00:03:08.919 --> 00:03:10.360
wouldn’t escape with its body intact.

00:03:10.919 --> 00:03:11.919
Who are you?

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:13.759
Wangxian Sect.

00:03:14.120 --> 00:03:15.800
Little Saint King, Lin Yue.

00:03:16.800 --> 00:03:17.879
So you know.

00:03:18.439 --> 00:03:19.240
Little Saint King.

00:03:19.840 --> 00:03:22.800
These are internal matters of our Shangqing Palace.

00:03:23.639 --> 00:03:25.199
As long as you don’t interfere,

00:03:25.639 --> 00:03:27.800
I’ll let you leave right away.

00:03:28.879 --> 00:03:29.360
Brother Lin.

00:03:30.719 --> 00:03:31.719
I accept your kindness.

00:03:32.759 --> 00:03:34.000
But you still have important matters to attend to.

00:03:34.919 --> 00:03:35.719
You should go.

00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:37.080
It’s fine.

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:38.879
Though my cultivation is shallow,

00:03:39.599 --> 00:03:41.280
dealing with these fools

00:03:41.479 --> 00:03:42.319
is no problem for me.

00:03:42.719 --> 00:03:43.479
Arrogant!

00:03:44.280 --> 00:03:45.319
You refuse to show respect.

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:48.199
Today, I’ll spill your blood here!

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:52.560
Brother Lin.

00:03:53.120 --> 00:03:54.400
You’re all at the Peak of the Samsara Realm.

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:55.520
You can’t fight unless you reach Transcendence.

00:03:56.319 --> 00:03:57.639
Then I’ll transcend.

00:04:03.800 --> 00:04:05.120
I’ve already crippled their cultivation.

00:04:05.319 --> 00:04:06.080
Whether to kill or spare them

00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:08.120
is up to Palace Master Qin.

00:04:09.280 --> 00:04:10.319
Spare us, Young Palace Master!

00:04:10.439 --> 00:04:11.599
Please spare us, Young Palace Master!

00:04:11.599 --> 00:04:12.879
Have mercy, Young Palace Master!

00:04:12.879 --> 00:04:13.719
Young Palace Master.

00:04:13.840 --> 00:04:14.800
I am already a cripple.

00:04:14.919 --> 00:04:17.360
Please show mercy, Young Palace Master.

00:04:17.480 --> 00:04:20.319
I, Qin Wunian, am the Palace Master of Biluo Shangqing Palace,

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:22.759
not a Young Palace Master.

00:04:25.720 --> 00:04:27.480
I know you were forced into this.

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:28.680
So today,

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:30.199
only the main culprits will be punished.

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:32.839
The rest of you can redeem yourselves in the future.

00:04:33.319 --> 00:04:34.839
Thank you, Palace Master, for sparing us.

00:04:35.000 --> 00:04:36.279
Thank you, Palace Master, for sparing us.

00:04:36.439 --> 00:04:37.959
Thank you, Palace Master, for sparing us.

00:04:47.639 --> 00:04:48.959
Who are you?

00:04:50.639 --> 00:04:51.519
Your Majesty, Demon Emperor.

00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:55.279
May your blessings and longevity match the heavens.

00:04:56.480 --> 00:04:57.639
Yiyi came to the Demon Emperor's palace.

00:04:57.639 --> 00:04:59.120
She was escorted all the way by this person.

00:04:59.800 --> 00:05:01.519
He wishes to serve under the Demon Emperor.

00:05:02.319 --> 00:05:03.360
Serve me?

00:05:03.800 --> 00:05:07.800
I am willing to serve you faithfully.

00:05:14.399 --> 00:05:15.040
Why?

00:05:19.480 --> 00:05:21.000
What makes you qualified?

00:05:22.639 --> 00:05:25.560
You want to be my servant?

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:32.079
Calm down.

00:05:33.360 --> 00:05:34.000
Sect Leader.

00:05:34.399 --> 00:05:35.360
Are you really going to just watch

00:05:35.360 --> 00:05:36.600
as Yiyi walks to her death?

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:42.199
Sister.

00:05:46.480 --> 00:05:46.959
Who?

00:05:57.759 --> 00:06:00.920
You must taste good.

00:06:05.600 --> 00:06:06.920
Let's talk somewhere else.

00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:20.439
Yiyi.

00:06:21.920 --> 00:06:22.639
What's going on?

00:06:23.639 --> 00:06:24.399
It's Lin Yue.

00:06:36.399 --> 00:06:37.399
Why is it you?

00:06:38.199 --> 00:06:39.680
Master told me to wait for you here.

00:06:41.519 --> 00:06:42.600
I won't go with him.

00:06:43.519 --> 00:06:44.439
You don't have to go with him.

00:06:59.120 --> 00:06:59.959
Right now,

00:07:02.920 --> 00:07:03.560
now,

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:04.680
now,

00:07:06.680 --> 00:07:07.560
now,

00:07:08.279 --> 00:07:10.399
I am now the Little Saintess of the Wangxian Sect.

00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:24.399
Outer Realm Teleportation Talisman.

00:07:24.839 --> 00:07:26.160
It dragged me to the Outer Realm.

00:07:26.720 --> 00:07:29.360
Who are you buying time for?

00:07:30.079 --> 00:07:30.800
Guess.

00:07:32.920 --> 00:07:33.639
Fine.

00:07:34.279 --> 00:07:36.560
Then I'll torture you bit by bit.

00:07:36.839 --> 00:07:38.040
I'll make you

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:40.199
wish you were dead from the pain.

00:07:40.639 --> 00:07:42.560
I do want to feel

00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:44.040
what pain is like.

00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:55.439
Too bad you're not the Great Emperor Qi Tian.

00:07:55.600 --> 00:07:57.879
Even with the Extinction Universe Staff,

00:07:58.279 --> 00:07:59.560
you can't hurt me.

00:08:00.560 --> 00:08:01.480
That's truly a pity.

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:08.040
I wish I could experience this world again.

00:08:11.240 --> 00:08:12.879
Wangxian Sect.

00:08:13.800 --> 00:08:14.920
Brother Lin, what are you doing?

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:19.120
One of my companions

00:08:19.920 --> 00:08:20.839
has sacrificed themselves.

00:08:21.720 --> 00:08:22.839
I still want to persuade you to turn back.

00:08:23.759 --> 00:08:25.040
Those who enter the Ink Dragon Array

00:08:26.040 --> 00:08:27.759
must endure trials of blades and fire.

00:08:28.120 --> 00:08:29.519
And suffer pain beyond breaking bones.

00:08:30.399 --> 00:08:31.800
This is my last hope.

00:08:44.840 --> 00:08:45.799
Too many people's hopes

00:08:45.799 --> 00:08:47.159
rest on my shoulders.

00:08:47.679 --> 00:08:48.799
I'm a pawn with no retreat.

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:51.759
I can only move forward.

00:08:58.320 --> 00:08:58.919
Brother Qin.

00:08:59.399 --> 00:09:00.240
You're playing me.

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:02.759
I'm only borrowing my descendant's appearance.

00:09:02.879 --> 00:09:04.840
So you are the Ink Dragon Emperor?

00:09:06.799 --> 00:09:08.440
Just a remnant soul.

00:09:13.279 --> 00:09:14.440
Senior, I came to

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:15.000
I know.

00:09:15.679 --> 00:09:16.639
My power

00:09:16.840 --> 00:09:18.600
is not what it once was,

00:09:19.159 --> 00:09:21.840
but it's still more than an ordinary Transcendence Realm can bear.

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:24.799
You need tendon-changing and marrow-washing to rebuild your bones.

00:09:25.519 --> 00:09:26.519
Are you ready?

00:09:36.759 --> 00:09:38.320
Before I cultivated immortality,

00:09:38.519 --> 00:09:40.720
I was just a small-time gambler in the mortal world.

00:09:41.480 --> 00:09:42.679
Since you've entered the array,

00:09:43.039 --> 00:09:44.159
let's gamble together.

00:09:49.720 --> 00:09:50.440
Place your bet.

00:09:52.759 --> 00:09:53.200
Big.

00:09:56.240 --> 00:09:57.720
One, two, three—small.

00:10:00.039 --> 00:10:00.720
You lost.

00:10:05.039 --> 00:10:08.600
Bone shattering means grinding all your bones to dust.

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:10.600
Only then can you forge indestructible bones.

00:10:10.759 --> 00:10:13.440
The pain far exceeds ordinary broken bones.

00:10:14.120 --> 00:10:15.360
Do you still want to continue?

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:18.360
Continue.

00:10:18.759 --> 00:10:19.200
Alright.

00:10:19.799 --> 00:10:20.320
Big.

00:10:22.720 --> 00:10:23.399
You won.

00:10:24.600 --> 00:10:25.519
As a reward,

00:10:26.080 --> 00:10:26.960
which bone shall be shattered?

00:10:27.080 --> 00:10:28.240
You choose.